Name: no long-term activity
Meaning: Much less than expected activity, or none at all, for this number over the past 90 days.

Name: high long-term activity
Meaning: More than expected activity for this number over the past 90 days.

Name: high short-term activity
Meaning: More than expected activity for this number over the last 24 hours.

Name: moderate long-term activity
Meaning: Expected activity for this number over the past 90 days.

Name: moderate short-term activity
Meaning: Expected activity for this number over the last 24 hours.

Name: sparse long-term activity
Meaning: Sparse, regular volume of verification traffic on this number over the past 90 days.

Name: continuous long-term activity
Meaning: Continuous, regular volume of verification traffic on this number over the past 90 days.

Name: very high long-term activity
Meaning: Very high volume of verification traffic on this number over the past 90 days.

Name: very high short-term activity
Meaning: Very high volume of verification traffic on this number over the past 24 hours.

Name: no activity
Meaning: Very low volume of verification traffic, or none at all, was ever observed on this number.

Name: low long-term activity
Meaning: Low volume of verification traffic on this phone number over the past 90 days.

Name: low short-term activity
Meaning: Low volume of verification traffic on this phone number over the past 24 hours. Very low volume of verification traffic, or none at all over the past 90 days.

Name: low activity
Meaning: Less than expected activity for this number.
